Package: ipbes.su.chap3.world.heritage
Type: Package
Title: IPBES Sustainable Use Assessment - Figure Chapter 3 - World Heritage List
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given   = "Nicolas",
           family  = "Casajus",
           role    = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email   = "nicolas.casajus@fondationbiodiversite.fr",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5537-5294")))
Description: Code to reproduce the Figure 'World Heritage List' of 
    the chapter 3 of the IPBES Sustainable Use Assessment. This figure shows 
    the global distribution of UNESCO World Heritage sites (both cultural and 
    natural) with an emphasis on their endangered status.
URL: https://github.com/ahasverus/ipbes-su-chap3-world_heritage
